<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-4436360c-3449-4937-b67d-9a7bffb1d26d'>
            
<p class="">55.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-6ff31206-4499-45a2-8f65-1c5e4e65534c">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-6ff31206-4499-45a2-8f65-1c5e4e65534c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-6ff31206-4499-45a2-8f65-1c5e4e65534c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-6ff31206-4499-45a2-8f65-1c5e4e65534c">
                Mr. W. Fletcher
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-6ff31206-4499-45a2-8f65-1c5e4e65534c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-01-18/debates/7078446b-c21f-45ed-9d03-06d1d61a9075/CottonIndustry#contribution-6ff31206-4499-45a2-8f65-1c5e4e65534c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the President of the Board of Trade whether he has considered the statement made in his annual report, of which a copy has been sent to him, by the president of the Lancashire Cotton Corporation; and whether he will now take the necessary steps to consider favourably the re-opening of the Liverpool Cotton Exchange.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6ff31206-4499-45a2-8f65-1c5e4e65534c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-01-18/debates/7078446b-c21f-45ed-9d03-06d1d61a9075/CottonIndustry#contribution-6ff31206-4499-45a2-8f65-1c5e4e65534c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-3b9e94ed-6a35-4b2a-8077-0ec74379cf42">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-3b9e94ed-6a35-4b2a-8077-0ec74379cf42">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-3b9e94ed-6a35-4b2a-8077-0ec74379cf42">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-3b9e94ed-6a35-4b2a-8077-0ec74379cf42">
                Mr. H. Wilson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-3b9e94ed-6a35-4b2a-8077-0ec74379cf42" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-01-18/debates/7078446b-c21f-45ed-9d03-06d1d61a9075/CottonIndustry#contribution-3b9e94ed-6a35-4b2a-8077-0ec74379cf42">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I have not received a copy of this report, but have seen a Press summary of it. When purchasing cotton, the Raw Cotton Commission are faced with currency difficulties in some markets and shortage of supplies or export restrictions in others. Whatever the arrangements for purchasing, these difficulties would exist, and I have no reason to suppose that the re-opening of the Liverpool Cotton Exchange, would assist matters in any way.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-3b9e94ed-6a35-4b2a-8077-0ec74379cf42" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-01-18/debates/7078446b-c21f-45ed-9d03-06d1d61a9075/CottonIndustry#contribution-3b9e94ed-6a35-4b2a-8077-0ec74379cf42">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-d54b8c9e-7e80-413b-8b8a-c7117e7424cb">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-d54b8c9e-7e80-413b-8b8a-c7117e7424cb">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-d54b8c9e-7e80-413b-8b8a-c7117e7424cb">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-d54b8c9e-7e80-413b-8b8a-c7117e7424cb">
                Mr. Fletcher
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-d54b8c9e-7e80-413b-8b8a-c7117e7424cb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-01-18/debates/7078446b-c21f-45ed-9d03-06d1d61a9075/CottonIndustry#contribution-d54b8c9e-7e80-413b-8b8a-c7117e7424cb">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is not the right hon. Gentleman aware that one of the leading personalities whose name was mentioned when the Liverpool Cotton Exchange was closed is a director of this new corporation that has now come out against it, and would he, therefore, himself reconsider the advisability of re-opening the Cotton Exchange at Liverpool and thus get over some of the handicaps that now exist?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d54b8c9e-7e80-413b-8b8a-c7117e7424cb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-01-18/debates/7078446b-c21f-45ed-9d03-06d1d61a9075/CottonIndustry#contribution-d54b8c9e-7e80-413b-8b8a-c7117e7424cb">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>







<div class="content-item other-content">
